column1: Baby Barnaby's////As far as the food goes
column2: some of the best brunch food I've ever had.  The green eggs are where it's at.  My plate was devoured with the quickness.  It comes with toast
column3: seasoned potatoes which reminded me of jack in the box curly fries but better and in little squares
column4: and a side of sausage.  The sausage was actually very flavorful.
